  "level": 0,
  "ordinal": 0,
  "summary": "Main\nFollowing previous discussions with panellists, users and the market, the BEISL board has approved the following proposed amendments to the benchmark tanker descriptions for speeds & consumptions, the port consumptions and associated TCE calculations. These changes are in line with the revised Guide To Market Benchmarks and our intention is to implement these changes from 1 May 2015 . VLCC\n13 knots laden on 70mt IFO\n12.5 knots ballast on 53mt IFO\nIncrease the discharge consumption to 110 tons.",
